{"tid":156372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇矮妹但又鍾意高佬？","createTime":"2017-03-14T16:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T16:47:30.000Z","uid":16046,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a8a1d5530312ab6d6cbcb9fce5098f10b177c17","tid":156372,"uid":16046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:20:57.000Z","msg":"我特別鍾意高佬，最好高過我。<br />\n有時佢地生得好高，錯覺以為好似好高竇，但其實內心都係一個大哥哥咁，我覺得見到一個咁高的男仔向你撤嬌特別好有滿足感。<br />\n<br />\n其實 高佬唔難溝 一定易溝過細細粒矮佬（好靚仔的除外）<br />\n加上一般黎講身高腳長 淨係腳都有排玩 <br />\n同埋 我又唔會因為矮過條仔感到自卑<br />\n反而矮都溝到高佬我覺得好威威😎<br />\n<br />\n不過 條仔太高用狗仔式比佢啪要佢就返高度 <br />\n要擘大啲自己對腳先插得入 老一輩會笑要擔櫈仔比人屌西 <br />\n<br />\n利申哈比人150cm <br />\n但男友186cm"},{"pid":"7bc04572c84262e4d411714a7e461b3f6a728f54","tid":156372,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:22:18.000Z","msg":"十個矮妹十個都鍾意高佬㗎啦"},{"pid":"6efa939b323d827ba5505999bb6df653042e6582","tid":156372,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十個矮妹十個都鍾意高佬㗎啦</blockquote><br />\n未必 高佬行埋黎會比佢氣勢嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你唔好踩扁我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6ff064ece23b660b8c69914d9b0523e965efa7","tid":156372,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:39:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十個矮妹十個都鍾意高佬㗎啦</blockquote><br />\n未必 高佬行埋黎會比佢氣勢嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你唔好踩扁我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚇親之後就鍾意"},{"pid":"8b2d11ee886fe852b7966cdb100775fd55df6610","tid":156372,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:44:03.000Z","msg":"狗仔式點啪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔用櫈得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de3e9a55baa8f5a24200b641732e6333f350d60","tid":156372,"